      "content": "okay, i have some hydrogen peroxide. so if i use that to clean it and then add a really thick layer of the manuka honey like you said, is that basically the same as getting it done professionally? i'm trying to avoid the stitches if i can since i'm on a budget and don't want to spend all day in a waiting room. if i do the peroxide and honey thing, i'll be safe right?",
